snippet.title: dsaf dli all endings 1:49:43.233 (to be improved)
snippet.description:
(copied from speedrun.com run description)

the run that no one expected! am i right? yes....? anyway this run was ass, its not perfect. YET.

I died on breadbear once or twice
I died on nightguard once
and died on Dave A LOT OF TIMES
and also fluked with saves files

this category can be pushed a lot further, i think the perfect time of this category will be 1:2x:xx or something like that, i can see it happening one day.

Am I going to improve this?

DEFINIETLY.

i just need to find time for that, like i said earlier it can be pushed even further. this run will stay for a while, atleast for now on.

i guess thats everything i wanted to say.

(this run was highly inspired from LamasareBRW's dsaf1 all endings run, shoutout to him, he will get sub 2 hour run one day, i can see it.)
